Package: mksv3
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}, python-qt4, python-qscintilla2, python-configobj, python-qt4-fresh1
Description: Simple programmers text editor
 Some of features:
  * Syntax highlighting for more than 30 languages
  * Bookmarks
  * Search and replace functionality for files and directories.
      Regular expressions are supported
  * File browser
  * Autocompletion, based on document contents
  * Hightly configurable

